CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Through FMF, its operating subsidiary, Kandal M Venture is a contract manufacturer of affordable luxury leather goods with its manufacturing operations in Cambodia. We primarily manufacture handbags, such as shoulder bag, crossbody bag, tote bag, backpack, top-handle handbag, satchel, and other smaller leather goods, such as wallets. Our customers are well-known global fashion brands that are headquartered in the United States.
